## 4. Components

### Buttons

| Variant | Background | Text | Border | Radius | Padding |
|---------|------------|------|--------|--------|---------|
| Primary | `--color-primary` | white | none | `8px` | `12px 24px` |
| Secondary | transparent | `--color-text` | `--color-border` | `8px` | `12px 24px` |
| Ghost | transparent | `--color-primary` | none | `8px` | `12px 24px` |
| Danger | `--color-error` | white | none | `8px` | `12px 24px` |

### Inputs

- Border: `1px solid var(--color-border)`
- Focus: `2px solid var(--color-primary)`, no outline
- Border radius: `8px`
- Padding: `10px 14px`
- Error state: border color `var(--color-error)`

### Cards

- Background: `var(--color-surface)`
- Border: `1px solid var(--color-border)`
- Border radius: `12px`
- Padding: `24px`
- Shadow: `0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`

